<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirm Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #1A1F71;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px;
        }
        .email-header img {
            max-width: 100px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-body h1 {
            color: #2B2B2B;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-body .name{
            font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-body p {
            color: #2B2B2B;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .email-body a {
            color: #1A1F71;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .email-footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2B2B2B;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #192b64;
            margin: 0 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-body h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .email-body p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749344/Component_23_kveaih.png" alt="Bizfides Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Email Verification!</h1>
            <p class="name">Dear {{firstName}},</p>
            <p>
                Thanks for signing up with Bizfides! We're excited to have you on board. To complete your registration and access our services, please verify your email address by clicking on the link below:
            </p>
            <p><a href={{verifyCode}}>www.bizfidesverify.com</a></p>
            <p>
                This step ensures that we can keep you updated on your account and services.
            </p>
            <p>
                If you have any issues or questions, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:bizfidessupport@gmail.com">bizfidessupport@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Bizfides Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <a href="#"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749394/Group_85_j0mzqd.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725457343/h2bx7ealhirzxfmeoezf.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749469/Group_87_x2fqro.png" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749428/Group_88_ihoec5.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
            <p>Copyright Â© 2024</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
